    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Quantity<Q> that)
      Compares this quantity to the specified Measurement quantity. The default implementation compares the Quantity.getValue() of both this quantity and the specified Quantity stated in the same unit (this quantity's unit).
      Specified by:

      Returns:
